      var sBox = document.querySelector('subject-box');
      function setUp() {
        sBox.subject = {
          name: 'subject name',
          connections: [],
          hypervideos: []
        };
      }
 
      suite('<subject-box>', function() {
        test('verify event "get-hypervideos" fired', function() {
          var eventFired = false;
          sBox.addEventListener('get-hypervideos', function(){
            eventFired = true;
          });
          setUp();
          assert.isTrue(eventFired);
        });
        test('defines the "subject" property', function() {
          setUp();
          assert.equal(sBox.subject.name, "subject name");
        });
      });
    </script>
